title: Chini Chor
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Chinese, Indian, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Vegetarian restaurant and sweet centre. Massive selection of savouries, curries and breads, including many varieties of paratha. Also South Indian and Desi Chinese (Indian versions of Chinese dishes) sections on the menu, and a juice bar. Vegans need to ask as the menu does not have explanations of the dishes.
